IIF([RSAF TABLE].[DESPDATE] IS NOT NULL,DATEDIFF(DAY,[RSAF TABLE].[RECDATE],GETDATE()),NULL) AS [Elapsed Time]
AND (([RSAF TABLE].[QUOTE REF DATE]) IS NULL))
